sentences: Burden of a Day was an American post-hardcore band, from Sarasota, Florida, formed in January 2000.
Burden of a Day was an American post-hardcore band, from Sarasota, Florida, formed in January 2000.
They played their last show in Sarasota on March 6, 2010.
Burden of a Day started as a worship band in church, until they were moved to reach out to people with their music.
Most of the members of Burden of a Day are still together, working on their new, untitled album.
This band is called Colours and currently have three songs released on YouTube: "The Illusionist", "The Machine", and "The Passenger".
The band formed in 2000 and signed to independent label Blood & Ink Records in 2005 for their debut full-length, which followed in 2006.
